WEBVTT

00:00:00.381 --> 00:00:02.365
Track 06.08

00:00:03.915 --> 00:00:04.974
Narrator: 1

00:00:06.138 --> 00:00:10.450
A: I need to make dinner for eight people!

00:00:10.847 --> 00:00:12.407
B: I can help you.

00:00:13.968 --> 00:00:15.053
Narrator: 2

00:00:16.534 --> 00:00:19.416
A: I need to go to the supermarket,

00:00:19.470 --> 00:00:21.339
but I’m really busy.

00:00:21.992 --> 00:00:23.050
B: I’ll go.

00:00:24.768 --> 00:00:25.482
Narrator: 3

00:00:26.840 --> 00:00:32.202
A: Oh no! I don’t have any money with me!

00:00:32.997 --> 00:00:34.214
B: I can pay.

00:00:36.089 --> 00:00:37.041
Narrator: 4

00:00:38.294 --> 00:00:42.306
A: I can’t open this bottle of water!

00:00:42.546 --> 00:00:43.780
B: I’ll do it.

00:00:45.623 --> 00:00:46.796
Narrator: 5

00:00:48.037 --> 00:00:50.356
A: I need to go to the shops.

00:00:50.524 --> 00:00:51.873
Can you drive me?

00:00:52.834 --> 00:00:55.611
B: Sorry, but I’m really busy.

00:00:56.079 --> 00:00:57.455
Jim can take you.

00:00:59.302 --> 00:01:00.387
Narrator: 6

00:01:01.542 --> 00:01:03.895
A: I need some cups.

00:01:03.920 --> 00:01:06.276
Do you have any cups?

00:01:06.740 --> 00:01:08.451
B: No, I don’t.

00:01:08.769 --> 00:01:10.700
I can give you some glasses.